==Korean==
===Noun===
'''무릎''' (mureup)
# [[knee]]
# [[lap]]

====Derived terms====
* 무릎 [[꿇다]] (-kkulhda) To [[bend]] the [[knee]]s, [[kneel]] (down), [[surrender]]
* 무릎 [[맞대다]] (-majdaeda, -matdaeda) To [[make friends]] (face to face, literally, knee to knee)  
* 무릎 [[치다]] (-chida) To [[slap]] on the knee to show a great surprise
* 무릎에 [[앉다]] (mureupE anjda) To sit on another's [[lap]] 
* 무릎을 [[베다]] (mureupEul beda) To [[pillow]] the head on another's [[lap]] 

